Cell["\<\
The Clifford group is generated by the Hadamard gates, the quadrant phase \
gates, and the CNOT (or CZ) gates. Here are the generators of the 3-qubit \
Clifford group.\
\>", "ExampleText",
 CellID->239031022,ExpressionUUID->"a9557ed3-c866-4e82-9b05-59b709fbe2db"],

